data.description: Beautiful brick home located minutes away from Chisholm trail toll is waiting on it's future owner! With its own private courtyard and covered front porch, private wrought iron gate leading to the front door, and mature trees, it’s got beautiful curb appeal—but that’s only the beginning. Because inside the property’s walls lies an interior that’s oozing with fresh new paint! This 5-bedroom-2 ½ bathroom-2-car garage setup comes with a living room and a a game room. Master bedroom is on the first floor with a garden tub, double sinks, separate shower and walk in closet. 2 additional guest bedrooms are downstairs, while one is split from the master bedroom, the other guest bedroom is a separate dwelling from the home which gives your guest more privacy and comfort. Upstairs you'll find 2 bedrooms, 1 full bathroom and a game room. But what completes its cozy, family-home aura are its hardwood flooring, beautiful chandelier and cozy fireplace. This home is vacant, and waiting on you!
